  - "Built exclusively to <span class=\"text-akro-3 font-semibold\">Level 3 standards</span>, all systems are redundant, ensuring extremely high availability. The strategic proximity to the Frankfurt Internet Exchange (DE-CIX) and optimal location on the Ingelheimer Aue provide excellent connectivity and infrastructure advantages."
